
Docker compose file template for one Enterprise Server and one Universual Forwarder,
deploy within the same host OS:
lenovo-network-telemetry-splunk-all-in-one-1+1.yml  

Docker compose file template for one Enterprise Server and two Universual Forwarder,
deploy within the same host OS:
lenovo-network-telemetry-splunk-all-in-one-1+2.yml

Seperate docker compose file template for Enterprise Server and Universual Forwarder,
deploy within the different or same host:
lenovo-network-telemetry-splunk-server.yml
lenovo-network-telemetry-splunk-forwarder.yml

